Version: 1.0
ProjectId: 48a65ce7-9e10-4d5c-99af-60765d2fdbf0

RestoreWorkspace: No
SaveWorkspace: No
AlwaysSaveHistory: No

EnableCodeIndexing: Yes
UseSpacesForTab: Yes
NumSpacesForTab: 2
Encoding: UTF-8

RnwWeave: Sweave
LaTeX: pdfLaTeX

StripTrailingWhitespace: Yes

BuildType: Package
PackageUseDevtools: Yes
PackageInstallArgs: --no-multiarch --with-keep.source
PackageCheckArgs: --no-vignettes --no-build-vignettes --ignore-vignettes  --no-examples --no-install
PackageRoxygenize: rd,collate,namespace
